The rationale behind this is `restjson` brings in many annoying dev-dependencies when using `cargo test`, so this speeds up the build `241` vs `294` on master.

Additional, `restjson` relies on tokio0.2 and panics with the new async API in 1.0 because we use tokio1 however we could use the blocking API...

